<h2>The Best of Both Worlds</h2>
<p>Bringing the unique, individualized and academically integrated Montessori approach into the New Hampshire public school system provides an ideal opportunity for K-6th grade children of all backgrounds and learning styles in Southern New Hampshire.</p>
<p><em>Mill Falls</em> students are united in mixed-age classrooms to learn with — and from — each other about the world and their place in it. This inspires a sense of connectedness and foster the values of peace and respect for others and our planet.</p>
